DefaultReaderConfiguration.fullDescription: Collects events from Oracle Database, including Select, Insert, Update, and Delete
DefaultReaderConfiguration.preQueryCheck: SELECT count(*) from DBA_AUDIT_TRAIL WHERE TIMESTAMP >= ?
DefaultReaderConfiguration.queryString: SELECT TIMESTAMP,dat.DBID,SESSIONID,ENTRYID,STATEMENTID,USERNAME,USERHOST,ACTION,RETURNCODE,ACTION_NAME,ADMIN_OPTION,AUDIT_OPTION,CLIENT_ID,COMMENT_TEXT,ECONTEXT_ID,GLOBAL_UID,dat.GRANTEE,INSTANCE_NUMBER,LOGOFF_DLOCK,LOGOFF_LREAD,LOGOFF_LWRITE,LOGOFF_PREAD,LOGOFF_TIME,NEW_NAME,NEW_OWNER,OBJ_NAME,OBJ_PRIVILEGE,OS_PROCESS,OS_USERNAME,OWNER,PRIV_USED,PROXY_SESSIONID,SCN,SES_ACTIONS,SESSION_CPU,SYS_PRIVILEGE,TERMINAL,TRANSACTIONID,dat.SQL_BIND,SQL_TEXT,dat.DBID,NAME FROM dba_audit_trail dat, v$database WHERE TIMESTAMP >= ? AND ROWNUM <= ? AND dat.dbid = v$database.dbid ORDER BY TIMESTAMP, SESSIONID, ENTRYID
